oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Music Unlimited Job No. 36815
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Accounting; Hatch Show Print (Firm); Snow, Hank;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Invoice (No. 1364) for an order placed for Music Unlimited by Abraham Hamza for 2 orders of 200 two color window cards (undated) for a performance by Hank Snow at the Peterborough Memorial Center in Peterborough, Ontario, Canada and at the Kitchner War Memorial in Kitchner, Ontario, Canada. Receipt indicates the agreed price, quantity, shipping method, and a description of the posters.
